Ndubuisi Orji, Abuja The Peoples Democratic Party ( PDP) on Monday demanded a review of the Supreme Court judgement of the 2019 polls. The Supreme Court had affirmed President Muhammadu Buhari as winner of the 2019 presidential election. The PDP is also demanding a review of the apex court judgement on the Kaduna, Kano, Kastina and Osun governorship polls. The opposition party spokesman, Kola Ologbondiyan stated this at a press briefing at the partyâ€™s national secretariat in Abuja.